item.description:
This is a Telephone Meetup. This Conderence call is for those members interested in participating in the Master Key System Study Group.

This first call on Oct 9th will be a Q&A about the study group. Topics include where to get copies of the book by Charles Haanel and what to expect
as a participant in the study group.

The next Study Group call will be on October 15th at 9pm and will discuss the book's introduction and the first chapter.

The number is: 605-990-0700 Access Code 1081150 #

We have established a Yahoo! group for this Mater key Study Group. Please join this group if you decide to participate. This yahoo group will share files, messages, and be the central mailing list for this study
group. The Yahoo Group is located at:

http://groups.yahoo.c...
